descript.abstract: This data layer represents municipalities for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Adams_Municipalities_2012.gdb.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for students, faculty, and staff of the University of Wisconsin-Madison for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement. View 'Adams_Municipalities_2012_Original.html' for complete metadata documentation.
